  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the fondue pot to 375 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Thread the white asparagus, chicken breast, and garlic onto skewers.",
    "Heat the olive oil in the fondue pot and add the skewers to cook for 5 minutes.",
    "Sprinkle the salt, black pepper, and lemon juice over the skewers and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Serve the skewers hot with shaved grana padano cheese and chopped parsley.",
    "Repeat the cooking process for the remaining skewers.",
    "Keep the fondue pot warm to maintain a consistent temperature.",
    "Monitor the temperature to prevent overheating."
